{
  "stem": "10699.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And with me, I come in here, I come in very late with it, I felt, from the very beginning, that death was on our doorstep.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said, really and truly, were we all meant to die.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I kept believing, because I needed something more than just fight for my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I needed to believe that it can't be that everybody will die.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I needed something to hold on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I was-- I remained a kind of believer, a believer in God.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Perhaps not in everything else, a believer in God.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I think, in my case, it helped me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In her case, it was the opposite.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That what she saw, she didn't-- there is no God.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If this can happen, there is no God.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Therefore, even to this day, she's a little bit more in need to go to a synagogue or something like this, but I don't know how much she still believes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because she lost, after all, her parents and her sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She died in Auschwitz on the night, in April, 1945.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She had tuberculosis, you didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "My brother, Armand, saw her before she died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She didn't make it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You see, she was separated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And, afterwards, she was all alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were with other French girl, Suzann, that was all the time with us, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We have to keep a certain-- we were always little groups together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You had to keep in little groups.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "If you were alone, then you went down very fast.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Some women were-- some were with mothers and daughters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I saw some of the very great Jewish families in France-- bankers, big stores holders, who were also finished off in Auschwitz, and did not survive.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
